==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fagaceae
<hw>Fagaceae</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>a natural family of chiefly
monoecious trees and shrubs, including beeches, chestnuts, and oaks; it
includes the genera <gen>Castanea</gen>; <gen>Castanopsis</gen>;
<gen>Chrysolepis</gen>; <gen>Fagus</gen>; <gen>Lithocarpus</gen>;
<gen>Nothofagus</gen>; and <gen>Quercus</gen>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> family <fam>Fagaceae</fam>, beech family.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

